c: 46
v: 29
t: "(Muhammad) sira nyaritakna nalikane Ingsun nekakake sak rombongan jin ngrungokake anggonira maca al-Quran Bareng Jin mau wis ngrungokake padha kondha, \"Para kancaku padha menenga ngrungokna unine al-Quran iki\". Bareng wis rampung pamacane, jin mau bali marang panggonane banjur mulang al-Quran marang kancane"